PREAMBLE
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
The AAMovies Ecosystem is not just a codebase; it is a meticulously 
architected, high-performance, 100% Native Android universe. Built 
with sweat, logic, and pure native power, it is designed to run 
flawlessly and generate revenue seamlessly. 

This custom license (JCEL) grants you immense freedom to utilize, 
clone, fork, and monetize this powerful engine. However, this freedom 
comes with one non-negotiable Golden Rule: RESPECT THE ARCHITECT. 
Proper attribution is not just requested; it is strictly required 
both in the source code and within the compiled application's User 
Interface (UI).

By cloning, downloading, compiling, or modifying any part of this 
repository, you explicitly agree to the terms and conditions outlined 
in this license.

ARTICLE 1: PERMISSIONS (WHAT YOU CAN DO)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Subject to the conditions outlined in Article 2, you are hereby granted 
a free, non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license to:

1.1. CLONE & FORK: You may clone the repository, create your own forks, 
     and use the underlying native architecture as the foundation for 
     your own movie, streaming, or content delivery applications.
1.2. MODIFY & ADAPT: You may alter the UI, change the colors, modify 
     the layouts, and adapt the backend Firebase schema to suit your 
     specific project needs.
1.3. COMMERCIALIZE & MONETIZE: You may completely replace the existing 
     Ad URLs (Pop-ups, Direct Links) with your own CPM networks, AdMob, 
     or any other monetization strategy. You are free to generate 
     unlimited personal revenue using this architecture.
1.4. DISTRIBUTE: You may compile the source code into APK/AAB files 
     and distribute them across any platform, including Google Play 
     Store, Amazon Appstore, Huawei AppGallery, or third-party sites.

