The permissions granted in Article 1 are strictly contingent upon 
fulfilling BOTH of the following attribution requirements. Failure to 
comply instantly terminates your rights under this license.

2.1. REPOSITORY ATTRIBUTION (THE CODE CREDIT)
     If you host, publish, or share a modified or unmodified version 
     of this source code publicly (e.g., on GitHub, GitLab, Bitbucket), 
     you MUST include the following text prominently at the very top 
