     > (https://github.com/The-JDdev)."

2.2. IN-APP ATTRIBUTION (THE VISUAL CREDIT) - [CRITICAL]
     You MUST include a visible credit to the original author within 
     the graphical User Interface (UI) of your compiled application 
     (both User App and Admin App). 
     
     This credit must be easily accessible to the end-user (for example, 
